Battera::

she dove down and then crained her neck to pull up at high speed. She 
came up under Ares and hit him with her wing, trying to knock him 
down.

Then did a tuck and roll, swooped down to CyberShark. "Look, see here 
handsome. I got left behind and I"m not getting left behind again. 
I'm going to fight with you, not matter what. And if you got words to 
say about it, tell me after the fight."
